1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,879
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:32,649
=Episode 4=
(As we passed each other,)

3
00:00:32,650 --> 00:00:36,170
(the urge to turn back shattered my hatred.)

4
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:52,420
She is my wife.

5
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:57,060
Trash like you doesn't get to touch her.

6
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:22,080
Now's not the time to rest.

7
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:23,839
If one Flower Slave came,

8
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,160
more will follow.

9
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,440
That was my sword spirit, Baobao.

10
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,880
I suffered heavenly backlash
and my powers are now gone.

11
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,920
She no longer has the strength
to leave the sheath.

12
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:34,520
Drag me into that pool

13
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:36,560
before they arrive.

14
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,440
(He might be able to wipe them out.)

15
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,720
(Better save him first.)

16
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,560
How long until you recover?

17
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,440
An hour.

18
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,399
A powerful enemy is at our door.

19
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,920
Drop your temper.

20
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,920
I'll hold them off.

21
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,280
You'd better hurry.

22
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,919
We only get one chance.

23
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,080
Go!

24
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,960
Ye Zhao, hurry!

25
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:54,200
I can't hold them much longer!

26
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,920
A bunch of fools courting death.

27
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,320
Zhang Muzhi.

28
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,960
You'd better hide well.

29
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:42,760
The moment I see you, you die.

30
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:55,680
You think I need help to fight a god?

31
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:50,059
(I'll search you inch by inch,)

32
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:52,400
(through your flesh and bones,)

33
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,800
until

34
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,640
I find your demon root.

35
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,760
(The Flower Slaves are outside.)

36
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,200
(And I have nowhere to go.)

37
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,440
(This is the safest place for me.)

38
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,119
(If I want to live,)

39
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,080
(I have to make him pity me.)

40
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:16,500
♪Once, the Nine Provinces shone
with brilliant lights♪

41
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:19,880
♪For you,
I brushed the snow from your robes♪

42
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,880
I was born into splendor,

43
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:25,080
raised in cruelty.

44
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,520
Now my mother is gone.

45
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,520
I have nothing left in this world.

46
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,800
If I die by your hand,

47
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,760
I'll have no regrets.

48
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:40,969
♪You are the snow
that rests on timeless hills♪

49
00:05:40,970 --> 00:05:42,639
♪You fall into my gaze♪

50
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,439
♪Yet mistaken for the moon♪

51
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,199
Do it.

52
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,689
♪I break through fate's cocoon♪

53
00:05:47,690 --> 00:05:51,550
♪travel a thousand miles to you♪

54
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:54,309
♪You are a night of falling petals♪

55
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:58,659
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

56
00:05:58,660 --> 00:06:05,089
♪Telling me not to long for you♪

57
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:07,799
♪You're a butterfly
drifting into dreams on the wind♪

58
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,499
♪Fading at my fingertips♪

59
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:11,759
♪Weaving endless longing♪

60
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:14,619
♪Leaving me alone with endless years♪

61
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:18,469
♪Bound by countless obsessions♪

62
00:06:18,470 --> 00:06:21,219
♪How could I ever forget your face♪

63
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:23,019
♪A lingering moon♪

64
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:25,459
♪A fleeting forever♪

65
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:27,109
♪All that remains♪

66
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:32,680
♪Is that one page
telling me not to long for you♪

67
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,640
(I won the gamble.)

68
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,320
(He really is soft-hearted.)

69
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,000
Are you going to talk or not?

70
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,479
General,

71
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,679
these Flower Slaves

72
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,799
are unusual.

73
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,640
We had the coroner examine them,

74
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:07,520
and he found their bodies packed
with root-like growths.

75
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,799
At night,

76
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,679
(Li Chengjiang, Imperial Guard of Ning)
these roots move through their veins,

77
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,479
causing them unbearable pain.

78
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,080
Human blood eases it,

79
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,120
at least a little.

80
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,120
In a way,

81
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,080
they're pitiful.

82
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,760
Pitiful?

83
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,760
I mean, the pitiful always
have something to be despised for.

84
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,760
Did you get anything out of them?

85
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,760
Not a word.

86
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,440
They don't seem human.

87
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,400
Leave.

88
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,919
I'll interrogate him myself.

89
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,080
Yes, General.

90
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,040
Does it hurt?

91
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,760
I've got nine more steel needles.

92
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,400
Tonight,

93
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,960
I'll drive them in one by one,

94
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,240
until you talk.

95
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,880
General,

96
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,879
you want to drive my people

97
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:18,560
out of Ning Capital.

98
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,960
Let's make a deal.

99
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,920
What do you think?

100
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,400
Who are you?

101
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,760
I'm the Clan Leader
of Flower Slaves Clan.

102
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:33,240
Help me capture one person,

103
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,639
and I swear

104
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:37,479
my clan will vanish

105
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,400
from Ning forever.

106
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,200
Who is it?

107
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,080
Tell me.

108
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:51,560
A woman cast out of the palace.

109
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,880
Chu Xihe.

110
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,000
Chu Xihe.

111
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,320
You abduct civilians,

112
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,200
throw the capital into chaos,

113
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,080
and now

114
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:10,120
you even dare set your sights
on Her Highness?

115
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,720
Who do you think you are,

116
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,880
to demand this death wish?

117
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,520
Bring me blood!

118
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:42,280
Pei Xiao.

119
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:45,480
I'll make you pay twice

120
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,760
for what you did today.

121
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:52,920
The Flower Slaves
are after Her Highness.

122
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,959
Send more men.

123
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,400
Capture every last one of them.

124
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,919
We must get there first.

125
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,080
Yes, sir!

126
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,720
(Her fever hasn't subsided,)

127
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,880
(and her qi is weak.)

128
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:12,000
(A hundred years ago,)

129
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,559
(I should have perished)

130
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:15,000
(with no chance of survival.)

131
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,760
(Yet now I'm completely unharmed.)

132
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,199
(I've regained a physical body.)

133
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,520
(and my powers have returned.)

134
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,480
(All of this...)

135
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,760
(Could it be because of you?)

136
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,640
(Stop overthinking.)

137
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,000
(That's impossible.)

138
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,400
(A hundred years ago,)

139
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,840
(you were the one who pushed me)

140
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,240
(into the abyss.)

141
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,440
Zhao.

142
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,400
Why?

143
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,960
Because,

144
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,120
I am a demon.

145
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,520
My soft-hearted god.

146
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:04,099
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

147
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:06,979
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

148
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:09,699
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

149
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:11,339
♪Let the long shadows♪

150
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:16,940
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

151
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,579
♪If in a dream♪

152
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:21,339
♪I can hear your voice♪

153
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:24,179
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

154
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:26,779
♪Let it be us♪

155
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:31,579
♪drawing endlessly close♪

156
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:33,339
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

157
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:35,980
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

158
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:38,939
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

159
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:40,579
♪Not even in time♪

160
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:46,259
♪to tell you how I feel♪

161
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:47,779
♪If the rain won't stop♪

162
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:50,539
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

163
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:53,499
♪Let love go on♪

164
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:56,059
♪Until forever♪

165
00:11:56,060 --> 00:12:00,699
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

166
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:03,299
♪Until forever♪

167
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:10,420
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
